This project integrates multiple Tableau worksheets into a unified analytical showcase — covering **macro economics**, **sales analytics**, and **business performance monitoring**.
- Demonstrates visualization of **KPI**, **trend**, **geospatial**, and **correlation** data  
- Simulates end-to-end analytical storytelling (EDA → Visualization → Insight)  
- Suitable for **data analyst**, **business intelligence**, and **risk monitoring** roles  

**Main Visual Components:**
- Boxplot for price distribution analysis  
- Geographic GDP and sales maps (China & USA)  
- Funnel chart for customer conversion and retention  
- Word cloud for product-level profit & sales  
- Scatter and bar charts for performance evaluation  
- Time-series trend and Pareto chart for sales insight  
